and there's also protocol too,

00:49:03.760 --> 00:49:06.610
evidently, that states can
sign, of course, saying OK,

00:49:06.610 --> 00:49:12.400
so a war between a state and
a responsibly-led armed group.

00:49:12.400 --> 00:49:16.870
So my question is
what do you see

00:49:16.870 --> 00:49:20.895
as the legal or actual
