00:49:20.895 --> 00:49:23.020
something a civil was as
opposed to something else,

00:49:23.020 --> 00:49:24.550
and also maybe speak
to the difference

00:49:24.550 --> 00:49:25.966
between the civil
wars and perhaps

00:49:25.966 --> 00:49:28.895
an insurrection
rebellion or revolution.

00:49:28.895 --> 00:49:29.770
